; Similar to Kojo's ColorMaker.linearGradient function
to kojoLinearGradient :x1 :y1 :color1 :x2 :y2 :color2 :cyclic?
	localmake "colorStops createPList2 [
		[0 :color1] [1 :color2]
	]
	localmake "spreadMethod "pad
	if :cyclic? [
		localmake "spreadMethod "repeat
	]
	output createLinearGradient [:x1 :y1] [:x2 :y2] :colorStops :spreadMethod
end